      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "是啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "这比看电视剧有趣",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "我还真的想到一件",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "高中的时候学校禁止早恋",
